"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-02-23-2024-olympic-qualifiers-cameroon-goalie-bihina-confident-of-victory-against-super-falcons\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  on  By  Indomitable Lionesses of Cameroon goalkeeper, Michaely Bihina is optimistic her side can beat fierce rivals Nigeria in their 2024 Olympic Games third round qualifier.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 127, \"end\": 134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999978572784803, \"rank\": 2.142224935056977e-06, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two teams will clash in the first leg tonight at the Stade de la Reunification, Douala.\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 278, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The reverse fixture is billed for the Moshood Abiola Stadium, Abuja next week Monday.\", \"from\": 280, \"to\": 365, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 318, \"end\": 332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moshood_Abiola\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Moshood Abiola\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moshood_Abiola\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moshood_Abiola\"}, {\"begin\": 342, \"end\": 347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuja\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.841986704830449e-20, \"text\": \"Abuja\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuja\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuja\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Indomitable Lionesses and Super Falcons have met 10 times in the past, with just wins for the former.\", \"from\": 367, \"to\": 472, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bihina, however, stated that the teams' head-to-head record matters little this time around.\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 566, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Personally, I am calm.\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 591, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We know that Nigeria are a great team, but we have what it takes to accomplish our mission\\\" the Racing Power FC of Portugal goalie told FIFA.com.\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 605, \"end\": 612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999978572784803, \"rank\": 2.142224935056977e-06, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 728, \"end\": 736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"FIFA.com\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our training sessions have been going well and the belief is there.\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 807, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now it's up to us to execute what we have worked on during our preparations.\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 884, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 20-year-old also highlighted the factors that could favour her side in the double header.\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 979, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Firstly, our squad, which is a mix of youth and experience.\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 1041, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bit by bit, things are coming together; we are developing understandings and making our build-up play second nature, while also perfecting more and more the tactical formations put in place by our coach Jean-Baptiste Bisseck,\\\"added Bihina.\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1281, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Secondly, I'd say the fact that we are all motivated.\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1337, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have frequently been unlucky in our games against Nigeria, so now it's time for that to change.\\\"\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1391, \"end\": 1398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999978572784803, \"rank\": 2.142224935056977e-06, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Doma United midfielder, Majalisa returns for Rangers clash  EPL: Hojlund to miss Fulham game, Manchester derby with injury  2026 WAFCON: 'It would not happen for other tournaments' - Super Falcons' Plumptre slams CAF  WAFCON 2026: Super Falcons Ajibade disappointed with postponement  WAFCON 2026: Super Falcons decamped after postponement  Friendly: Cameroon coach gives reason for defeat to Super Falcons  Friendly: Babajide relishes Super Falcons' win over Cameroon  Friendly: Super Falcons floor Cameroon 3-1 in Yaounde  Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1484, \"end\": 1491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rangers_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999888587, \"rank\": 1.0970722212261467e-11, \"text\": \"Rangers\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rangers_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rangers_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1520, \"end\": 1526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fulham_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999998684347788, \"rank\": 1.3151425580782815e-07, \"text\": \"Fulham\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fulham_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fulham_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1652, \"end\": 1655, \"title\": \